  "display_name": "linguistics and terminology studies",
  "description": "This cluster of papers encompasses theoretical and applied studies in terminology and specialized language, including cognitive linguistics, ontologies, corpus linguistics, semantic relations, conceptual variation, lexical semantics, knowledge representation, and multidimensionality. The papers explore the dynamics of terminological variation, the processing of terms in specialized communication, and the representation of multidimensional and multimodal information in specialized domains.",
